		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well like, this has been very informative, I used to think that it was only the top and bottom rows that were invisible, but apparently the actionsafe region of the screen is two rows from the bottom/top edges, and one column from the left/right edge. Titlesafe would be 1 row/column inwards from those edges.

		

